Description: Delivering your transactional and marketing email through one reliable platform.
Name: SendGrid

Methods.Name: Delete Contacts
Methods.Description: Deletes a single or multiple contacts.

Methods.Name: Upsert Multiple Contacts
Methods.Description: Add or update multiple contacts. Can also be used to add contacts to a list.

Methods.Name: Upsert Contact
Methods.Description: Add or update a contact. Can also be used to add a contact to a list.

Methods.Name: Send Template Mail
Methods.Description: This option allows you to send a mail based on a template.

Methods.Name: Send Mail
Methods.Description: This option allows you to send a mail by providing either HTML or plain text content.

Methods.Name: Add to Global Suppression
Methods.Description: This endpoint allows you to add one or more email addresses to the global suppressions group.

Methods.Name: Add to Group Suppression
Methods.Description: This endpoint allows you to add email addresses to an unsubscribe group.

Methods.Name: Delete Contact From Marketing List
Methods.Description: Removes a contact from a Marketing list.

Methods.Name: Get List Contacts
Methods.Description: Gets the contacts in a list.

Methods.Name: Delete Contact From List
Methods.Description: Deletes a contact from a list.

Methods.Name: Add Contact To List
Methods.Description: Adds a contact to a list.

MetaTile: SendGrid Integration | Email Marketing Automation | Cyclr
MetaDescription: Automate your SendGrid marketing campaigns & list management by building marketing automation workflows with Cyclr's drag and drop integration builder.
Content: Provide your users with integration to SendGrid, giving them easy to install premade automation workflows to sync data between your application and SendGrid.
